rson writes AL-JALEE-LO with musk, saffron, rose and sugar on bread for 7 days and eat and give one bread daily in charity then he will be beloved and respected among the creatures.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh jo shakhs 7 din tak AL-JALEE-LO ko Musk o Zaafraan, Gulab aur Shakkar se Naan par likh kar khaa le, aur rozaana ek naan sadqa de is naam ki barkat se Khalaaeq (makhlooq) mein azeez o mohtaram hoga.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جو شخص 7 روز تک ’’اَلْجَلِیْلُ‘‘ کو مشک و زعفران، گلاب اور شکر سے نان پر لکھے اور کھالے، اور روزانہ ایک نان صدقہ دے تو اس نام کی برکت سے خلاق میں عزیز و محترم ہوگا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": nu